data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  Beautifully renovated 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom + office, pool home on a large corner lot in the desirable NW neighborhood of Robin Lane!  This home offers four spacious bedrooms, office, living room with wood burning fireplace, family room, dining room, and a large kitchen that overlooks the private lanai with screened in pool.  HUGE backyard!  Recent upgrades including a new roof and HVAC system ensure peace of mind for years to come.  Home also features new flooring throughout, upgraded bathrooms, new plumbing and interior paint.  With no HOA fees, you'll have the freedom to customize and enjoy your property without restrictions.  Located in the desirable NW neighborhood of Robin Lane, you'll benefit from proximity to top-rated schools, parks, shopping, dining, and major transportation routes.   Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a turnkey, beautifully renovated pool home in a great location of town. Schedule a showing today and make this dream home yours!
